OL,3,C'Ronan's Law' to introduce stricter
OL,4,Crules on knife retailers
OL,6,FStricter rules for retailers selling
OL,7,Fknives online, along with tougher
OL,8,Fpenalties for those who break the
OL,9,Frules, have been announced by the home
OL,10,Fsecretary.
OL,12,FYvette Cooper announced unveiled a
OL,13,Fraft of anti-knife crime plans,
OL,14,Fincluding making retailers report bulk
OL,15,For suspicious sales to police, and
OL,16,Fincreasing the jail sentence for
OL,17,Fselling weapons to children or illegal
OL,18,Fblades such as zombie knives, to two
OL,19,Fyears.
