OL,3,C'Ronan's Law' to introduce stricter
OL,4,Crules on knife retailers
OL,6,FThe laws will collectively be known as
OL,7,F'Ronan's Law', named after 16-year-old
OL,8,FRonan Kanda who was murdered in
OL,9,FWolverhampton in 2022.
OL,11,FRetailers will be required to report
OL,12,Fany bulk or suspicious-looking
OL,13,Fpurchases of knives on their platforms
OL,14,Fto police to prevent illegal resales
OL,15,Fhappening across social media accounts.
