OL,3,C'Ronan's Law' to introduce stricter
OL,4,Crules on knife retailers
OL,6,FThe sentence for selling weapons to
OL,7,Funder 18s will also increase from six
OL,8,Fmonths to a maximum of two years
OL,9,Fprison time, which could apply to an
OL,10,Findividual who has processed the sale
OL,11,For a CEO of the company.
OL,13,FThe law will also cover legal and
OL,14,Fillegal knives meaning the possession
OL,15,Fof any offensive weapon with intent
OL,16,Ffor violence will come with a maximum
OL,17,Fprison sentence of four years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
