OL,3,C'Ronan's Law' to introduce stricter
OL,4,Crules on knife retailers
OL,6,FThe government is also exploring
OL,7,Fwhether to introduce a registration
OL,8,Fsystem so only responsible retailers
OL,9,Fare allowed to sell knives.
OL,11,FIt comes after the government has
OL,12,Falready announced a strengthening of
OL,13,FID checks required to buy knives or
OL,14,Fhave them delivered.
OL,16,FThe home secretary thanked the Kanda
OL,17,Ffamily paying tribute to their work in
OL,18,Fhelping bring about knife crime reform.
