OL,3,C'Ronan's Law' to introduce stricter
OL,4,Crules on knife retailers
OL,6,FCooper said: "We are honouring our
OL,7,Fcommitment to introduce Ronan's Law in
OL,8,Fmemory of Ronan Kanda who was
OL,9,Ftragically killed in 2022.
OL,11,F"I am so grateful to the Kanda family
OL,12,Ffor their endless perseverance in
OL,13,Fensuring governments take the right
OL,14,Factions to protect young people from
OL,15,Ffurther tragedy."
